research_municipality_step.notes: Bunker Hill Village is a Type A General Law City governed by a Mayor and five Council Members elected at large. Mayor Keith Brown was elected in 2025. Councilmember Josh Pratt was elected in 2025. Councilmember Andrew Poor was appointed in May 2024. Councilmember Carl Moerer was elected in 2022. Councilmember Eric Thode was appointed in May 2019. Councilmember Susan Schwartz has served on the City Council since 2006.
